	<text>
		<body>
			<div type="transcription">
				<p>From: Consul <persName ref="#ehri_dr_yamaguchi">Yamaguchi</persName> (<placeName ref="#vienna">Vienna</placeName>)</p>
				<p>To: Foreign Minister <persName ref="#ehri_dr_mamoru_shigemitsu">Shigemitsu Mamoru</persName> (<placeName ref="#tokyo"
						>Tokyo</placeName>)</p>
				<p>
					<date when="1944-02-29">Since 29</date>th of last month, the control of <term ref="#t864" type="subject">Jews</term> in <placeName
						ref="#vienna">Vienna</placeName> has become even harsher. </p>
				<p> The following is what we learned in extreme confidentiality. Those who <term ref="#t582" type="subject">married Jews</term> are
					confined to<term ref="#t553" type="subject"> certain houses</term>; Those with <term ref="#t374" type="subject">mixed Jewish
						blood</term> are not allowed to join the <orgName ref="#g388">Arbeitsfront</orgName> or are <term ref="#t332" type="subject"
						>expelled</term> from it.</p>
			</div>
		</body>
